  36,12,"It is certainly We Who resurrect the dead, and write what they send forth and what they leave behind. Everything is listed by Us in a perfect Record"
  36,13,"Give them an example ňĻO Prophetňļ of the residents of a town, when the messengers came to them"
  36,14,"We sent them two messengers, but they rejected both. So We reinforced ňĻthe twoňļ with a third, and they declared, ‚ÄúWe have indeed been sent to you ňĻas messengersňļ.‚ÄĚ"
  36,15,"The people replied, ‚ÄúYou are only humans like us, and the Most Compassionate has not revealed anything. You are simply lying!‚ÄĚ"
